preference.name: WRKFLW_GraphViews.Workflow
preference.preference_description: Specifies the list of view names for "Workflow" tab in the client. The view names are defined in Workflow UI configuration file, which is stored in the dataset named by the value of preference "WRKFLW_graph_legend_configuration_file_name". This is a site preference.
